scx-scheds-harper for Debian
----------------------------

To use these schedulers:
1. Ensure your kernel supports sched_ext (check /sys/kernel/btf/vmlinux).
2. Edit /etc/default/scx to select your scheduler (default: scx_rustland).
3. Run 'systemctl start scx' to activate.

You can verify the active scheduler by running:
    cat /sys/kernel/sched_ext/root/ops_name

 -- Harper <https://github.com/Bacon-O/scx-scheds-harper>